summary: This Second Amendment to Lease, dated November 13, 2025, between 681 Gateway Center LLC and Twist Bioscience Corporation, expands the leased premises to include the third floor of the building, corrects the rentable square footage of the first floor, and extends the lease term through June 30, 2036. The amendment also details the commencement and rent commencement dates for the expansion premises, along with associated construction and abatement periods.
